<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165043428512">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165043119394">
<p id="fs-id1165043119396">Use the first derivative test to find all local extrema for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mroot><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mroot><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mroot><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mroot><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165043305742">
<p id="fs-id1165042982077"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>f</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> has no local extrema because <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mo>&#8242;</mo></msup></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msup><mi>f</mi><mo>&#8242;</mo></msup></annotation-xml></semantics></math> does not change sign at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
