<p id="fs-id1165042608705">The only critical point of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>f</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> is <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
