<p id="fs-id1165043319017">For the following exercises, analyze the graphs of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mo>&#8242;</mo></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msup><mi>f</mi><mo>&#8242;</mo></msup><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> then list all intervals where</p>
<ol id="fs-id1165043319031" type="a">
