<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042367880">
<p id="fs-id1165042367883">a. Increasing over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>&#8722;2</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>&#8722;1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>&#8722;2</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>&#8722;1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> decreasing over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>&#8722;2</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>&#8722;2</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>&#8722;1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>&#8722;1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> b. maxima at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>&#8722;1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>&#8722;1</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> minima at <math xmlns="http://www.w3