<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042364617">
<p id="fs-id1165042364619">Concave up for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> concave down for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> inflection points at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
