<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042364259">
<p id="fs-id1165042364262">a. Increasing over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> decreasing over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> b. Minimum at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> c. Concave up for all <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>x</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> d. No inflection points</p>
