<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165043327634">
<p id="fs-id1165043327636">a. Increases over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> decreases over <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> b. Minimum at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> maximum at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> c. Concave up for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo>&#8722;</mo><mfrac><mn>3<