<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042708181">
<p id="fs-id1165042708183">a. Increasing for all <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>x</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> where defined b. No local minima or maxima c. Concave up for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> concave down for <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> d. No inflection points in domain</p>
