<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042707190">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042707192">
<p id="fs-id1165042707194">There is no absolute maximum at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
